{"_path":"/maps/_ai/multimodal","_dir":"_ai","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"多模态 (Multimodal)","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"多模态-multimodal"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多模态 (Multimodal)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"gpt-4o端到端多模态标杆"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GPT-4o：端到端多模态标杆"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GPT-4o 是 OpenAI 的端到端多模态模型，\"o\"代表 Omni（全能）。不同于传统的拼接式架构，它在单一神经网络中统一处理文本、图像、音频，实现真正的跨模态理解和生成。在视觉理解、数学推理、语言理解等基准上全面领先，是 2025 年商业多模态模型的事实标准。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://openai.com/index/hello-gpt-4o/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GPT-4o 技术报告"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/gpt-4o-vs-google-gemini-ultimate-ai-showdown-2025-gary-fowler-octpe","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GPT-4o vs Gemini 对比"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"gemini-15-pro长上下文多模态王者"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gemini 1.5 Pro：长上下文多模态王者"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Google DeepMind 的 Gemini 1.5 Pro 支持百万级 Token 上下文，可一次性处理数小时视频、整本书籍或多张高分辨率图像。采用 Mixture-of-Experts (MoE) 架构，在多模态推理和长文档理解上表现优异，是企业级多模态应用的首选。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/pro/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gemini 1.5 Pro 技术报告"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"qwen25-vl开源视觉语言模型领先者"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Qwen2.5-VL：开源视觉语言模型领先者"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"阿里云的 Qwen2.5-VL 系列是开源视觉语言模型的标杆，覆盖 3B 到 72B 参数规模。支持图像、视频、文档理解，在 OCR、图表解析、视觉推理等任务上媲美商业模型。2025 年推出的 Qwen3-VL 进一步提升了多模态推理能力，是开源社区的首选方案。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/QwenLM/Qwen2.5-VL","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Qwen2.5-VL GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.bentoml.com/blog/multimodal-ai-a-guide-to-open-source-vision-language-models","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Qwen3-VL 介绍"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"llava-next学术界的开源先锋"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLaVA-NeXT：学术界的开源先锋"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLaVA（Large Language and Vision Assistant）将 CLIP 视觉编码器与 LLM 连接，开创了开源视觉问答的先河。LLaVA-NeXT 支持更高分辨率（336x336+）、多帧视频理解、LoRA 微调。2025 年的 LLaVA-OneVision 进一步优化了视频理解能力，是学术研究和快速原型开发的首选。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/LLaVA-VL/LLaVA-NeXT","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLaVA-NeXT GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/html/2509.23661v3","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLaVA-OneVision 论文"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"生成模型stable-diffusion-与-audiocraft"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"生成模型：Stable Diffusion 与 AudioCraft"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Stable Diffusion 3 是开源文本到图像生成的标杆，采用改进的 Diffusion 架构，支持 ControlNet 可控生成和 LoRA 快速定制。AudioCraft 是 Meta 的音频生成套件，包含 MusicGen（文本生成音乐）、AudioGen（文本生成音效）和 EnCodec（神经音频编解码），开源了完整的音频生成流程。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://stability.ai/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Stable Diffusion"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/facebookresearch/audiocraft","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AudioCraft GitHub"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"语音识别whisper"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"语音识别：Whisper"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"OpenAI 的 Whisper 是开源语音识别的标杆，支持 99 种语言的多语言语音识别和语音翻译。鲁棒性优异，能处理口音、背景噪音和技术术语。v3 版本进一步提升了多语言性能和推理速度，是语音应用的基础设施。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/openai/whisper","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Whisper GitHub"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"多模态-rag-与-agent"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多模态 RAG 与 Agent"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多模态与 RAG、Agent 结合是 2025 年的前沿方向。CLIP 和向量数据库实现图像语义检索，Qwen2.5-VL 和 GPT-4o 实现视觉感知 Agent，可处理 UI 自动化、文档分析、视频监控等复杂任务。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/html/2507.01925v1","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Vision-Language-Action Models 综述"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_51175703/article/details/148561284","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多模态学习路线"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"gpt-4o端到端多模态标杆","depth":2,"text":"GPT-4o：端到端多模态标杆"},{"id":"gemini-15-pro长上下文多模态王者","depth":2,"text":"Gemini 1.5 Pro：长上下文多模态王者"},{"id":"qwen25-vl开源视觉语言模型领先者","depth":2,"text":"Qwen2.5-VL：开源视觉语言模型领先者"},{"id":"llava-next学术界的开源先锋","depth":2,"text":"LLaVA-NeXT：学术界的开源先锋"},{"id":"生成模型stable-diffusion-与-audiocraft","depth":2,"text":"生成模型：Stable Diffusion 与 AudioCraft"},{"id":"语音识别whisper","depth":2,"text":"语音识别：Whisper"},{"id":"多模态-rag-与-agent","depth":2,"text":"多模态 RAG 与 Agent"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:multimodal.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/multimodal.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/multimodal","_extension":"md"}